DANH MC T VIT TT
- WSNs: Mng Cm bin Khng dy (Wireless Sensors Network)
- IoTs: Internet Vn vt (Internet of Things)
- nt Sink: nt mng Tp hp d liu
- nt Sensor: nt mng Cm bin Thu thp d liu
- CD: D liu Quan trng (Critical Data)
- RD: D liu Ph thng (Regular Data)
- instance: M loi bn tin
- Thut ton xp lch TOML: Thut ton xp lch Ti u Khe thi gian p
dng Hc my (Timeslot Optimization applying Machine Learning)
- RPL: Giao thc nh tuyn cho Mng Nng lng v Mt mt thp
(Routing Protocol for Low Power and Lossy Network)
- DAG: th C hng Khng Tun hon (Directed Acyclic Graph)
- Thut ton OF0: Hm mc tiu Tr s khng (Objective Function Zero)
- Thut ton MRHOF: Hm mc tiu tr (Hysteresis Objective
Function)
- ETX: Gi tr c lng chi ph truyn ti
- TSCH MAC: Giao thc Phn khe Nhy knh trn tng iu khin Truy
cp D liu (Time Sloted Channel Hop Protocol in Media Access Control
Layer)
- Tc v Tx: Tc v gi tin (Transmit)
- Tc v Rx: Tc v nghe v nhn tin (Receive)
- Tc v S: Tc v ng (Sleep)
- Sender-based: Hng gi tin
- Receiver-based: Hng nhn tin
- PDR: T l truyn nhn thnh cng (Packet Delivery Ratio)
- PLR: T l mt gi tin (Packet Loss Ratio)
- Latency: tr
- c ch RL MAC: C ch hc my tng cng trn tng iu khin
Truy cp D liu (Reforcement Learning in Media Access Control Layer)
- VMWare: Phn mm m phng H iu hnh VMWare Workstation
- Chun Z1: Chun Zolertia
- ASN: s Khe thi gian Tuyt i (Absolute Slot Number)

CHNG 1. XY DNG C CH TRUYN THNG A MC
TIU TRN TSCH-MAC
Trong chng ny, em s cp chi tit ti nhng ci tin trn RPL, giao thc
TSCH cng nh xy dng thut ton lp lch p dng k thut hc my thc
hin cc mc tiu trnh by Chng 1 v da trn nhng c s l thuyt
trnh by cng chng .
1.1 Truyn thng a mc tiu trong Mng cm bin Khng dy
1.1.1 Mng cm bin khng dy
Mng Cm bin Khng dy (WSNs) l mt mng Internet ni b m trong
cha cc n v gi nhn tin nm v tr a l khc nhau. n v c gi l
mote, node hay l nt mng v l cc thit b cm bin s dng cc lin kt
khng dy (v tuyn, hng ngoi hoc quang hc) phi hp thc hin nhim
v thu thp thng tin d liu phn tn vi quy m ln. Trong cc WSNs thng
thng, c mt nt c gi l nt Sink c vai tr tp hp d liu v gi ti cc
n v qun l gim st trc tip hay gin tip [1]. Cc nt gi d liu cho nt
Sink c gi l nt Sensor.
WSNs c nhc im l kh nng x l, lu tr v tng tc ca cc nt mng b
gii hn bi ti nguyn v cc nt mng thng bit lp v b gii hn v nng
lng. Chnh v l do , cc nh khoa hc lun mun ci tin cc c ch hot
ng bn trong WSNs nhm gip chng hot ng hiu qu hn v thc hin
nhiu tc v hn trong iu kin b gii hn ngt ngho v lun vn ny cng gii
quyt vn gia tng hiu nng ca nt trong mng WSNs [2].
1.1.2 Bi ton truyn thng phn cp
Theo thi gian, vic truyn thng ngy cng phc tp vi ngy cng nhiu thnh
phn tham gia trao i d liu trn WSNs [7]. Vai tr v tm quan trng ca cc
thnh phn cng c s khc bit v i hi s phn chia ti c s u tin cho d
liu ca bn vai tr quan trng hn trong bi ton m n v s dng mng IoTs
cn gii quyt s c nhiu ti nguyn hn.
Chng hn, bi ton ng dng IoTs kh ph bin hin nay l bi ton y t thng
minh. y l bi ton m yu cu truyn thng phn cp sm nht ng vai tr
quan trng trong hot ng h thng y t [7]. C th, d liu v y t c hai loi
hnh d liu l d liu tnh trng khn cp s dng trong nhng tnh hung cp
cu v d liu tnh hung bnh thng. Do din tin ca cc ca cp cu thng
din ra rt nhanh v nh hng ln ti tnh mng ngi bnh, yu cu truyn ti
nhanh chng d liu tnh trng khn cp tr nn sng cn vi mng IoTs trong
h thng y t thng minh [7]. Tuy nhin, ti nguyn mng IoTs c hn, nn trong
nhiu trng hp, h thng phi phn phi ti nguyn c s phn cp m truyn
thng d liu tnh trng khn cp phi c m bo u tin nhn ti nguyn
cn thit pht huy ht cng sut truyn ti ca mnh, gim tr v mt mt
gi tin, nhm gip cc bn lin quan n ca cp cu c c thng tin nhanh
nht v chnh xc nht, a ra quyt nh kp thi cu sng sinh mng bnh

nhn. Vi cc d liu thuc loi bnh thng, min l vic truyn ti din ra n
nh, vic gia tng tr v gim tin cy l c th chp nhn c.
Trong cc bi ton truyn thng phn cp, s c t hai tr ln loi d liu c
u tin truyn ti khc hon ton nhau. Vic gim hiu nng ca truyn thng
loi d liu c u tin cao s nh hng tiu cc n vai tr ca ton h thng
IoTs trong ng dng m n phc v hay nh hng trc tip n tng thnh phn
hoc ton mng IoTs . Chnh v l do , cc c ch trong mng IoTs thay v
dn u ti nguyn cho mi c ch truyn thng, n phi chp nhn tp trung ti
nguyn vo cc truyn thng d liu c u tin cao v chp nhn hy sinh hiu
nng ca truyn thng d liu c u tin thp hn. Bn tin instance 1 s c
gi l Bn tin quan trng (Critical Data hoc CD) cn bn tin instance 2 s c

phn cp h thng th tn dng c ch sn c ca thut ton xp lch Orchestra.

n phc v cho nhng mc tiu sau:
- Phc v truyn thng phn cp: Cc bn tin d liu cm bin trong

- m bo hiu nng mc tt nht: Cho d ti nguyn dnh cho truyn

1.2 Xy dng c ch nh tuyn hai ng truyn vi RPL
1.2.1 Khi qut v RPL
Nh mi h thng mng Internet khc, WSNs l mt mng Internet phc tp v
c ch v phn tn v khng gian a l, khi m mt s nt Sensor c khong
cch xa nt Sink v khng th gi d liu trc tip cho nt ny. Do , cc giao
thc nh tuyn ra i cho php cc nt c th gi tin tc gin tip cho nhau
thng qua cc nt th ba hoc cc thnh phn mng khc thng qua c ch gi l
lu tr v chuyn tip [4]. C ch ny cho php xy dng mt tuyn ng tru
tng t nt ch n nt ngun ngoi vng ph sng ca nhau qua cc nt
trung gian trong vng ph sng ca nhau sao cho hiu qu nht bng cch
chuyn tip qua cc nt trung gian trong vng ph sng ca nhau ti nt ch.
Cc nh khoa hc thit k ra giao thc mi dnh ring cho WSNs, c gi l
Giao thc nh tuyn cho Mng Nng lng v Mt mt thp (Routing Protocol
for Low Power and Lossy Network - RPL) tn dng m hnh Sink Sensor
ti u nh tuyn d liu. Qua , vic nh tuyn s t chc theo cu trc d
liu dng cy thay v cu trc d liu dng th nh cc giao thc nh tuyn
truyn thng vn c chi ph x l lu tr v x l d liu ln hn. C th, cy
nh tuyn c gi l th C hng Khng Tun hon (Directed Acyclic
Graph DAG) c nt gc l nt Sink c nhn nhn nh nt gc mc 0 l nt
Sink v cc nt Sensor cn li l cc nt con, nt chu cc mc cao hn. Hai
nt kt ni n nhau (quan h cha con) phi m bo c th truyn nhn d liu
trc tip cho nhau (trong vng ph sng ca nhau) [3]. Hnh 1.1 s ch ra nguyn
l ny.
Hnh 1.1: Cy DAG da trn mng WSNs
Lu k hiu Hnh 1.1, nt nn trng ch en l nt Sink, nt nn en ch
trng l nt Sensor, ng k khng c mi tn biu th hai nt c th trao i d
liu trc tip cho nhau khng cn chuyn tip qua nt trung gian trong khi ng
k c mi tn hai u biu th quan h cha con ca hai nt trong cy DAG (hai
nt c th thc hin hop vi nhau) [3]. Cng cn lu thm rng m hnh mng
WSNs bn phi Hnh 1.1 l m hnh vt l cn cy DAG l s tru tng.
Mi cy DAG c th c nhn nhn nh ng i ca d liu t nt Sensor c
th ti nt Sink v mt m hnh mng cng hon ton c th c nhiu hn mt
cy DAG. T Hnh 1.1 ta cng c th thy chng ta c th xy dng nhiu cy
DAG cho mt Mng WSNs. Vic xy dng cy s ph thuc vo cc thut ton
4
nh tuyn. Hin nay, hai thut ton nh tuyn c s dng trong giao thc

ton chi ph da trn mc ca nt cha trong cy DAG m khng quan tm n
cc yu t khc. C th, mc nt cha tim nng m cng cao th chi ph gia nt
cha tim nng v nt tnh ton s cng cao. iu ny nhm hn ch d liu t nt
phi i nhng tuyn ng vng di hn, qua nhiu nt trung gian hn trc
khi n nt Sink. Trong khi , thut ton MRFOF tnh ton chi ph gia hai nt
chi ph truyn ti gia hai nt c c lng di gi tr ETX. Bng 1.1 s so
snh s khc v ging nhau gia hai thut ton nh tuyn l thut ton MRHOP
v thut ton OF0.

1.2.2 xut c ch truyn thng phn cp
Tut ton MRHOF tp trung vo bm st tnh trng ca WSNs nn nh tuyn s
dng thut ton MRHOF s t hiu nng cao hn thut ton OF0 vn tp trung
vo s n gin trong tnh ton. Tuy nhin, cho d thut ton MRHOP c tnh
ton phc tp hn thut ton OF0, phc tp ny l khng lm gim ng k
hiu nng mng. Tn dng tnh cht khc bit gia thut ton MRHOF v thut
ton OF0, vic phn chia knh truyn s din ra nh sau:
- Truyn thng D liu Quan trng nh tuyn theo thut ton MRHOF.
- Truyn thng D liu Ph thng nh tuyn theo thut ton OF0.
Nh vy vic truyn thng bn tin c u tin cao hn s s dng thut ton
nh tuyn hiu qu hn l thut ton MRHOF cn bn tin c u tin thp s
s dng thut ton nh tuyn km hiu qu hn l thut ton OF0. Nh vy,
truyn thng hai bn tin c u tin khc nhau s c ng truyn khc nhau, t
c th dn tri vic truyn tin trn cc tuyn ng khc nhau trong WSNs,

CHNG 2. TH NGHIM M PHNG
Trong chng ny, th nht em s trnh by ton b qu trnh xy dng v trin
khai cc ci tin trn RPL, giao thc TSCH v thut ton xp lch TOML t c
s l thuyt trnh by Chng 2 trn th vin m ngun m phng hot
ng WSNs tn l contiki-master. Th hai, em s trnh by qu trnh trin khai
th vin m ngun ln mi trng H iu hnh Contiki vi cng c Cooja
cng nh ci t cc cng c khc thu thp d liu th nghim. Th ba, em s
trnh by cc c im, mc tiu cng nh cc kch bn th nghim v cui cng
l phn tch kt qu th nghim.
2.1 Mc tiu th nghim
Mc tiu ca cc th nghim thut ton xp lch TOML trn giao thc TSCH bao
gm nhng ni dung sau:
- Hin thc ha thut ton xp lch TOML trn giao thc TSCH di dng
m ngun v cu trc d liu. Vic xy dng s k tha m ngun sn c
ca cc th vin m phng WSNs t doanh nghip v IoTs uy tn m
bo m ngun c tnh thc tin cao, cng nh c nhiu c hi nghin cu
thm v mng WSNs hin ti.
- Cho chy WSNs m phng v thut ton xp lch TOML trn giao thc
TSCH theo di qu trnh hot ng ca lp xp lch nh cc tc v
c gn, d liu u vo tnh ton c. ng thi, trong qu trnh chy
mng cng s tin hnh ci tin thut ton, thay i tham s.
- Thut ton xp lch TOML ra i nhm thay th thut ton xp lch
Orchestra, do , chng minh tnh ng n v cn thit ca vic thay
th thut ton xp lch ny vi thut ton xp lch Orchestra th cn phi
o c hiu nng mng vi cc thng s c th nh PDR v tr cng
vi so snh vi hiu nng ca WSNs vi quy m, mi trng v kin trc
mng tng t nhng s dng thut ton xp lch Orchestra. Ngoi ra,
vic so snh cng cn tin hnh trong nhiu th nghim vi cc WSNs c
quy m, mi trng v kin trc mng khc nhau kim nghim tnh u
vit ca thut ton xp lch TOML trong mi hon cnh thc t v mi
loi mng. Cng t c th tip tc phn tch v khm ph thm cc
kiu cu hnh tham s khc cho mng ph hp vi c th khc nhau.
Vic th nghim l cn thit v quan trng hin thc ha v mt m ngun
nhng c t l thuyt v thut ton xp lch TOML trn giao thc TSCH, cng
nh chng minh tnh ng n, thc tin v chng minh s u vit so vi thut
ton xp lch s b thay th l thut ton xp lch Orchestra thng qua cc s liu
o hiu nng c th vi WSNs m phng nhiu iu kin khc nhau. chiu
ngc li, cng t nhng th nghim m phng m c th b sung hon thin l
thuyt, khm ph ra cc m hnh mi, nhm tit kim cng sc v thi gian cho
cc giai on nghin cu pht trin trong tng lai.

2.2 Gii thiu v H iu hnh Contiki v mi trng Cooja
Contiki l mt h iu hnh m ngun m, c Adam Dunkels gii thiu vo
nm 2002 [18] p ng nhu cu pht trin ngy cng tng ca cng ngh IoT.
Vic s dng Contiki l mt la chn ti u trong xy dng th nghim m
phng thut ton xp lch TOML v s khng phi xy dng li t u cc d liu
m phng mng (s tiu tn nhiu thi gian v cng sc v quan trng l hon
ton khng cn thit) m k tha t nhng d liu sn c ci tin, pht trin
thut ton xp lch mi trong khong thi gian ngn nhng vn m bo tnh
chnh xc v hiu qu [19]. Cu to, h iu hnh Contiki bao gm 2 phn c bn
nh sau:
- Mi trng ContikiInstant: tng t nh cc h iu hnh khc trn nn
tng Linux, mc ch cung cp giao din (thng qua ca s lnh Terminal
hoc API) ngi dng tng tc vi h iu hnh Contiki. Lu ,
khng ch cc chng trnh m phng mng, bt k phn mm no khc
chy trn nn tng Linux u chy c trn H iu hnh Contiki. Bn
thn Contiki cng tch hp sn mt s phn mm nh trnh duyt mng
FireFox hay phn mm bt gi tin Wireshark,
- Th vin m ngun contiki-master: cung cp cc m ngun cn thit
thc hin cc gi lp v IoTs v WSNs. Cc m ngun c vit ch yu
bng ngn ng lp trnh C++ nhng cng cho php tch hp ngn ng lp
trnh Java v ngn ng lp trnh Python. Mi s xy dng, pht trin v
m phng u c thc hin trn th vin m ngun.
Cooja mt phn mm Phn mm ng vai tr Giao din cho php nhng nh
pht trin c th tng tc trc tip vi th vin contiki-master, xy dng cc
kch bn v tin hnh cc th nghim m phng. Cooja c vit bng ngn ng
lp trnh Java cng nh s dng th vin swing nn m bo s gn nh trong
m ngun. Mt s u im ca Cooja bao gm [20]:
- C kh nng gi lp cc mi trng truyn thng vi nhng c im v
kh truyn tin khc nhau bao gm: Mt mt c nh bng Phng php
th a Euclidean, Mt mt theo khong cch bng Phng php th

Vi tt c nhng ni dung em trnh by trong lun vn, cc thy c cng nh

d) Phng php nghin cu.

Lp lun l thuyt da trn cc c s l lun giao thc RPL, TSCH k thut hc

Trong khi , trong th nghim m phng gi lp hot ng WSNs h iu hnh
Contiki trn my o VMWare, th vin m ngun uy tn m phng hot ng

Qua phn tch mc ch th nghim l so snh WSNs gia thut ton xp lch
TOML v c ch a nh tuyn vi thut ton xp lch Orchestra, t , cng
vic cn lm l xy dng WSNs ci TOML cng nh ci thut ton xp lch
Orchestra vi hai cu hnh khc nhau l Sender-based v Receivered-based
nhng cc thng s khc phi ging nhau. Tip n, chng minh s u vit

e) Kt lun
Lun vn gm hai phn l xy dng c s l thuyt v th nghim m phng.
C s l thuyt vi ba ci tin ln l thc hin a nh tuyn trn RPL, thc hin
truyn thng phn cp trn TSCH-MAC v xy dng thut ton xp lch TOML
p dng k thut hc my. Vi c ch a nh tuyn giao thc RPL truyn

ngn v khng phi tranh thng lng vi truyn thng RD c nh hng
ng truyn khc. Trong khi , vi truyn thng tch bit, xung t gia bn
tin CD v RD s b loi b khi cc khe thi gian ch chp nhn truyn thng d
liu mt instance c th v thi gian ch ca cc bn tin CD s thp hn RD khi
s khe thi gian chp nhn truyn thng d liu CD nhiu hn RD. Vi vic xy
dng thut ton xp lch TOML p dng k thut hc my trong bi ton phn
loi a lp nt mng gn cc tc v ngu nhin trn mt khe thi gian, sau
tnh ton t l thnh cng ca cc tc v v quyt nh tc v no l ti u trn
khe thi gian trong mt khung khe v gn tc v ti u trong sut thi gian
di, m bo mng hot ng tt nht trong phm vi c th ca thut ton xp
lch TOML.
